long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tuberack makes it effortless to save and organize your YouTube videos. With just a click, you can add individual videos or entire playlists directly from YouTube into custom folders. Keep your content tidy, find what you need instantly, and easily rearrange videos between folders as your tastes evolve. Perfect for binge-watchers, students, creators, and anyone who wants a cleaner way to manage their favorite YouTube content.

Key Features:
- Save individual videos or full playlists with one click
- Create custom folders for easy organization
- Quickly relocate videos between folders for flexible curation
- Streamlined interface integrated right into YouTube
- Make your YouTube library truly yours with Tuberack.
